    {
      "instruction": "<p>Slice the<strong> rested pork </strong>on a clean chopping board and serve on top of the<strong> cooked rice</strong>, then pour the<strong> Tex-Mex style spiced tomato sauce</strong> on top</p><p>Serve with the <strong>spicy corn salsa</strong> to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
